Welcome to the Department of Commerce, Bureau of Export Administration (BXA),
Nonproliferation and Export Control Cooperation (NEC) Program. Our team works
     to strengthen foreign national export control systems to facilitate
 legitimate trade in high-technology goods, and to keep nuclear, biological,
    and chemical weapons out of the hands of terrorists and rogue states.

